OL,3,CMother and son rescued from tiny
OL,4,CIndonesian island days after shipwreck
OL,6,FRescuers in eastern Indonesia found a
OL,7,Fstranded mother and son on a remote
OL,8,Funinhabited island after their
OL,9,Fpassenger boat sank last week, with
OL,10,Fover a dozen people still missing.
OL,12,FThe 46-year-old woman and her 24-year-
OL,13,Fold son were found stranded on
OL,14,FBalaloho Island, one of the islands in
OL,15,Fthe Selayar Island chain that is part
OL,16,Fof Indonesia.
OL,18,FLocal media reported the mother and
OL,19,Fson pair clung to a makeshift raft
OL,20,Fbefore they washed up on the small
OL,21,Fisland that is around a mile long.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
