OL,3,CMother and son rescued from tiny
OL,4,CIndonesian island days after shipwreck
OL,6,FAnother group of five survivors were
OL,7,Ffound clinging to a raft in open water.
OL,9,FA search and rescue team retrieved
OL,10,Ffive survivors on Saturday evening,
OL,11,Fincluding a seven-year-old girl, who
OL,12,Fwere clinging to a fish trap.
OL,14,FAt least one person was confirmed dead.
OL,16,FThe KM Nurul Salsa, which was carrying
OL,17,F78 passengers and crew, experienced
OL,18,Fengine failure and sank on Wednesday
OL,19,Fabout 43 miles from the port in the
OL,20,FSelayar Islands, in South Sulawesi
OL,21,FProvince.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/4
