OL,3,CMother and son rescued from tiny
OL,4,CIndonesian island days after shipwreck
OL,6,FMore than 200 rescuers made up of
OL,7,Flocal police, fishermen and residents
OL,8,Fjoined the Indonesian army in
OL,9,Fassisting with rescue operations, said
OL,10,FAndi Sultan, head of the emergency
OL,11,Fresponse in Makassar.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,18,F"Rescue teams also faced extremely
OL,19,Fharsh weather conditions, including
OL,20,Fwaves as high as 2`3 meters and strong
OL,21,Fwinds," he added,
