OL,3,CMother and son rescued from tiny
OL,4,CIndonesian island days after shipwreck
OL,6,FPassenger boats are a common form of
OL,7,Ftransportation in Indonesia, an
OL,8,Farchipelago with more than 17,000
OL,9,Fislands. Lax safety standards and
OL,10,Fproblems with overcrowding frequently
OL,11,Fresult in accidents.
OL,13,FThe ship that sank on Wednesday
OL,14,Fofficially only had 50 people on
OL,15,Fboard, but it was carrying over a
OL,16,Fdozen extra passengers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/4
